5
00:01:43,910 --> 00:01:44,910
This is not something we can afford to be careless about.

6
00:01:44,910 --> 00:01:46,229
If she appears at the door the next moment,

7
00:01:46,229 --> 00:01:47,630
I'd die, no kidding.

8
00:01:47,630 --> 00:01:48,310
Seriously.

9
00:01:48,400 --> 00:01:49,000
You have no idea

10
00:01:49,000 --> 00:01:50,630
that I have not slept well for the past few days.

11
00:01:50,800 --> 00:01:52,360
I have nightmares every night.

12
00:01:53,080 --> 00:01:54,270
It's here, I think.

13
00:01:56,039 --> 00:01:56,870
Zhou Siyue

14
00:01:57,870 --> 00:01:59,190
Song Ziqi, open the door.

15
00:02:00,270 --> 00:02:02,310
Song Ziqi, open the door.

16
00:02:02,590 --> 00:02:04,000
I know you're here.

17
00:02:04,080 --> 00:02:05,720
Don't hide in there and not speak!

18
00:02:06,040 --> 00:02:07,000
Song Ziqi

19
00:02:09,190 --> 00:02:10,110
Open the door.

20
00:02:13,110 --> 00:02:14,360
Shut up.

21
00:02:14,880 --> 00:02:15,720
Song Ziqi

22
00:02:16,520 --> 00:02:18,030
Song Ziqi. Get the heck out.

23
00:02:19,110 --> 00:02:20,550
I know you are here.

24
00:02:21,110 --> 00:02:22,240
Come out now.

25
00:02:28,800 --> 00:02:30,270
You are being suspended, so what?

26
00:02:30,720 --> 00:02:33,000
Do you have to hide here and get so sullen about it?

27
00:02:33,440 --> 00:02:35,520
Get out of the bathroom!

28
00:02:52,600 --> 00:02:53,320
Hello.

29
00:02:54,390 --> 00:02:55,670
You douchebag! You...

30
00:02:57,960 --> 00:02:59,030
There's no need to...

31
00:02:59,030 --> 00:02:59,910
Don't stop me.

32
00:02:59,910 --> 00:03:01,670
Shadi, calm down first.

33
00:03:01,720 --> 00:03:02,670
You two get out.

34
00:03:03,110 --> 00:03:04,470
I want to talk to him alone.

35
00:03:04,880 --> 00:03:05,550
No...

36
00:03:06,670 --> 00:03:07,360
No, you...

37
00:03:22,390 --> 00:03:23,440
How about

38
00:03:24,670 --> 00:03:26,160
I take you back to school?

39
00:03:33,880 --> 00:03:36,440
My bag is still in there.

40
00:03:40,360 --> 00:03:42,240
I'd better wait outside.

41
00:03:48,880 --> 00:03:50,160
Can't you go easy on me?

42
00:03:50,160 --> 00:03:52,270
If you hurt me, I won't be able to become a pilot.

43
00:03:53,670 --> 00:03:55,240
You still want to be a pilot?

44
00:03:55,440 --> 00:03:56,550
Aren't you trying to stay away from everyone?

45
00:03:56,720 --> 00:03:57,829
Aren't you running away?

46
00:03:59,630 --> 00:04:00,630
You didn't pick up your phone.

47
00:04:01,670 --> 00:04:02,800
Your QQ is off-line.

48
00:04:04,160 --> 00:04:05,000
And you just sent me a message,

49
00:04:05,030 --> 00:04:06,600
telling me that I should never try to find you.

50
00:04:07,000 --> 00:04:08,360
Song Ziqi, who do you think you are?

51
00:04:08,520 --> 00:04:10,240
Why did you treat me like that?

52
00:04:10,390 --> 00:04:11,030
I am sorry.

53
00:04:11,190 --> 00:04:12,390
Sorry?

54
00:04:14,080 --> 00:04:15,550
You are just being suspended.

55
00:04:15,600 --> 00:04:16,829
Big deal?

56
00:04:17,040 --> 00:04:18,670
Do you need to avoid me like the plague?

57
00:04:18,760 --> 00:04:20,160
Calm down.

58
00:04:20,160 --> 00:04:21,510
I can't calm down.

59
00:04:22,600 --> 00:04:24,550
Can't you just man up?

60
00:04:26,550 --> 00:04:28,440
You said you wanted to be with me.

61
00:04:30,550 --> 00:04:32,720
You said you wanted to be a pilot.

62
00:04:33,070 --> 00:04:35,320
And it was you who insisted on our long-distance relationship.

63
00:04:36,550 --> 00:04:38,830
And now, something went wrong.

64
00:04:39,230 --> 00:04:41,270
All you want to do is to hide. Not dare to confront it.

65
00:04:41,510 --> 00:04:43,070
Song Ziqi, are you still a man?

66
00:04:43,200 --> 00:04:44,110
Enough!

67
00:05:02,160 --> 00:05:02,880
Ding Xian

68
