82
00:05:51,950 --> 00:05:53,720
Are you kidding me?

83
00:05:55,670 --> 00:05:57,440
Go back, please.

84
00:05:57,550 --> 00:05:58,920
I am not going back.

85
00:05:59,510 --> 00:06:01,510
I can't let you run away anymore.

86
00:06:03,670 --> 00:06:05,790
So, are you here to save me?

87
00:06:08,390 --> 00:06:09,110
I...

88
00:06:10,230 --> 00:06:11,790
I came for the money!

89
00:06:12,880 --> 00:06:13,760
What money?

90
00:06:13,880 --> 00:06:15,040
100 yuan for a kiss.

91
00:06:15,440 --> 00:06:17,160
You can count how many times you kissed me.

92
00:06:18,950 --> 00:06:19,640
Hold on.

93
00:06:23,510 --> 00:06:24,670
Enough?

94
00:06:25,830 --> 00:06:27,480
If it is not enough, I will give you my credit card.

95
00:06:27,880 --> 00:06:29,920
Take it.

96
00:06:32,440 --> 00:06:33,440
You douchebag!

97
00:06:46,790 --> 00:06:47,760
Thank you.

98
00:06:48,790 --> 00:06:50,440
I will pay you back later.

99
00:06:51,830 --> 00:06:52,670
No need.

100
00:07:11,350 --> 00:07:12,230
Shadi

101
00:07:17,040 --> 00:07:18,110
Did you see Shadi?

102
00:07:19,070 --> 00:07:20,110
Isn't she inside?

103
00:07:20,200 --> 00:07:21,040
No, she just rushed out.

104
00:07:21,110 --> 00:07:21,760
Did you see her?

105
00:07:21,950 --> 00:07:22,830
No.

106
00:08:06,040 --> 00:08:07,350
Call her.

107
00:08:07,510 --> 00:08:08,640
She won't pick up.

108
00:08:10,440 --> 00:08:11,600
What are you guys doing?

109
00:08:12,600 --> 00:08:13,270
Shadi

110
00:08:14,110 --> 00:08:15,070
I am sorry. It was my fault.

111
00:08:15,230 --> 00:08:17,000
I wasn't thinking straight. That wasn't me.

112
00:08:17,200 --> 00:08:18,110
I am sorry, Shadi.

113
00:08:18,230 --> 00:08:19,000
Song Ziqi, let go of me.

114
00:08:19,070 --> 00:08:19,880
No, I won't.

115
00:08:20,200 --> 00:08:20,790
No.

116
00:08:21,670 --> 00:08:23,350
You don't know anything but running around.

117
00:08:24,720 --> 00:08:25,880
If something really happens to you,

118
00:08:29,550 --> 00:08:30,070
I...

119
00:08:31,270 --> 00:08:32,470
You, what about you?

120
00:08:34,549 --> 00:08:35,789
I... I also don't know.

121
00:08:52,670 --> 00:08:54,880
If Ding Xian is really not around me anymore,

122
00:08:56,230 --> 00:08:58,110
I think I will be so scared.

123
00:09:08,640 --> 00:09:09,550
Let me do it.

124
00:09:09,910 --> 00:09:11,110
No need for the courtesy with me.

125
00:09:13,230 --> 00:09:14,200
I am leaving. Don't cry alone

126
00:09:14,350 --> 00:09:15,790
in the basement.

127
00:09:24,000 --> 00:09:25,030
You should speak out

128
00:09:25,670 --> 00:09:26,790
the things you need to say.

129
00:09:29,280 --> 00:09:30,320
Got it.

130
00:09:32,000 --> 00:09:33,520
Xianxian, I miss you so much.

131
00:09:33,520 --> 00:09:34,520
Me too.

132
00:09:34,910 --> 00:09:37,670
Maybe you guys should stay for two more days.

133
00:09:37,840 --> 00:09:38,840
That's not okay.

134
00:09:39,080 --> 00:09:41,230
If we stay for two more days, Song Ziqi will run away again.

135
00:09:41,640 --> 00:09:42,470
And,

136
00:09:42,760 --> 00:09:45,200
we should let him get back and apologize to his parents at least.

137
00:09:46,400 --> 00:09:48,030
I don't think he'll dare to do it again.

138
00:09:48,200 --> 00:09:49,280
Rest assured.

139
00:09:50,280 --> 00:09:51,470
Then, you...

140
00:09:51,640 --> 00:09:52,350
Zhou Siyue,

141
00:09:52,910 --> 00:09:55,110
if anything happens to Xianxian,

142
00:09:55,150 --> 00:09:56,520
I will come back and get you.

143
00:09:57,320 --> 00:09:58,030
Don't worry.

144
00:09:58,640 --> 00:09:59,440
She'll not get lost.

145
00:09:59,760 --> 00:10:00,590
Glad to hear it.

146
00:10:04,640 --> 00:10:05,760
You, come over.

147
00:10:06,080 --> 00:10:06,960
What?

148
00:10:07,910 --> 00:10:10,200
So, are we good now?

149
00:10:11,350 --> 00:10:12,440
Are you dreaming?

150
00:10:12,880 --> 00:10:14,110
How long have I been searching for you?

151
00:10:14,470 --> 00:10:16,590
You need to make it up to me twice as much.

152
00:10:20,710 --> 00:10:21,640
We are leaving now.

153
00:10:22,080 --> 00:10:23,110
Be safe. Bye.

154
00:10:23,440 --> 00:10:24,320
Don't cry.

155
00:10:25,440 --> 00:10:26,470
Hurry up.

156
00:10:27,000 --> 00:10:27,790
Take care.

157
00:10:40,640 --> 00:10:42,000
Let me take you back to school.

158
00:10:44,640 --> 00:10:47,080
No need. I can walk back to school myself.

159
00:11:28,230 --> 00:11:29,470
I'd leave now.

160
00:12:29,710 --> 00:12:31,470
If you are busy in school,

161
00:12:32,200 --> 00:12:33,840
you don't need to come here so frequently.

162
00:12:34,150 --> 00:12:35,790
Your mom and I are fine.

163
00:12:37,960 --> 00:12:39,280
I can spare some time.

164
00:12:40,960 --> 00:12:41,760
Right.

165
00:12:43,880 --> 00:12:45,840
Ding Xian is also in Hua Qing now.

166
00:12:51,320 --> 00:12:52,710
I like this girl.

167
00:12:54,110 --> 00:12:55,590
She has a spirit.

168
00:12:56,280 --> 00:12:57,200
Extraordinary.

169
00:13:05,280 --> 00:13:06,760
I'm holding you up.

170
00:13:08,280 --> 00:13:10,030
I didn't mean that.

171
00:13:14,790 --> 00:13:16,670
It is just that I don't think it is the right time yet.

172
00:13:16,910 --> 00:13:18,960
What do you mean, "not the right time"?

173
00:13:19,550 --> 00:13:22,280
When is the right time then?

174
00:13:27,590 --> 00:13:28,760
When I was young,

175
00:13:30,840 --> 00:13:33,110
I needed to go to Jiangling to teach.

176
00:13:33,790 --> 00:13:37,200
I wanted to take you and your mom with me.

177
00:13:37,640 --> 00:13:39,030
But your mom,

178
00:13:39,640 --> 00:13:42,200
since she was used to living a stable life,

179
00:13:42,470 --> 00:13:45,030
she didn't want to move around with me.

180
00:13:46,230 --> 00:13:48,000
I thought that as a family,

181
00:13:48,200 --> 00:13:50,640
we shouldn't live separately in two different places.

182
00:13:53,000 --> 00:13:54,590
But she was stubborn.

183
00:13:55,790 --> 00:13:57,440
She wouldn't agree no matter what.

184
00:13:58,320 --> 00:14:00,960
In the end, we dropped this matter.

185
00:14:02,320 --> 00:14:03,440
Regarding this,

186
00:14:04,280 --> 00:14:05,790
we have argued

187
00:14:06,400 --> 00:14:08,400
for many times.

188
00:14:10,030 --> 00:14:11,280
I used to think

189
00:14:12,280 --> 00:14:14,670
that she wouldn't be able to carry on in Shenhai,

190
00:14:14,880 --> 00:14:16,550
raising you all by herself.

191
00:14:16,640 --> 00:14:18,590
She would come to me one day.

192
00:14:19,350 --> 00:14:20,670
Only later did I find out

193
00:14:22,670 --> 00:14:24,030
that I had underestimated her.

194
00:14:25,400 --> 00:14:27,550
Not only did she bring you up,

195
00:14:28,470 --> 00:14:30,670
but also raised you to be such an excellent man.

196
00:14:31,960 --> 00:14:34,440
I don't know, for so many years,

197
00:14:35,030 --> 00:14:36,760
how much she has been through

198
00:14:37,790 --> 00:14:39,110
and how much she has suffered.

199
00:14:41,400 --> 00:14:42,880
Not until this accident

200
00:14:44,350 --> 00:14:45,880
did it dawn on me

201
00:14:47,280 --> 00:14:49,230
that your mom has always been

202
00:14:49,440 --> 00:14:50,960
a capable woman.

203
00:14:51,590 --> 00:14:53,000
In order to take care of me,

204
00:14:54,080 --> 00:14:56,520
she put away the obsession for so many years

205
00:14:56,790 --> 00:14:59,880
and came to Jiangling,

206
00:15:00,590 --> 00:15:02,440
busy around without a single complaint.

207
00:15:03,440 --> 00:15:04,520
Every time,

208
00:15:06,320 --> 00:15:08,910
I see her sleep when she is exhausted,

209
00:15:09,590 --> 00:15:10,590
I would think,

210
00:15:11,760 --> 00:15:14,470
why did I have to come to Jiangling

211
00:15:14,640 --> 00:15:16,440
to be a professor?

212
00:15:18,590 --> 00:15:19,670
Why did I

213
00:15:23,520 --> 00:15:27,080
have to keep her waiting for me?

214
00:15:34,760 --> 00:15:35,710
Let's get inside.

215
00:15:36,000 --> 00:15:37,280
There is a draft here.

216
00:15:37,550 --> 00:15:39,000
You may catch a cold.

217
00:15:45,470 --> 00:15:46,520
I believe,

218
00:15:48,840 --> 00:15:50,640
wherever my son goes,

219
00:15:51,230 --> 00:15:53,350
he will be successful.

220
00:15:53,760 --> 00:15:55,670
But I don't want you

221
00:15:56,350 --> 00:15:57,280
to find

222
00:15:57,320 --> 00:15:59,470
that you are all alone

223
00:16:00,280 --> 00:16:02,910
after you succeed.

224
00:16:07,550 --> 00:16:08,840
Don't make your mom and me

225
00:16:09,960 --> 00:16:11,670
an excuse of your own business.

226
00:16:12,320 --> 00:16:13,470
We are great.

227
00:16:13,910 --> 00:16:15,000
You don't need to worry about us.

228
00:16:19,080 --> 00:16:20,000
Alright.

229
00:16:20,640 --> 00:16:22,000
Go back if you don't have other things.

230
00:17:01,910 --> 00:17:02,840
Boss,

231
00:17:03,440 --> 00:17:05,520
you finally admit.

232
00:17:06,310 --> 00:17:09,230
I knew it! You have feelings for Ding Xian all along!

233
00:17:09,760 --> 00:17:10,640
Fine.

234
00:17:11,349 --> 00:17:12,589
Just tell me whether you will help me or not.

235
00:17:12,760 --> 00:17:14,430
Of course.

236
00:17:14,680 --> 00:17:16,680
I am good at chasing girls.

237
00:17:22,230 --> 00:17:23,560
Hello, guys.

238
00:17:23,920 --> 00:17:26,710
We are Love Chasing League from now on.

239
00:17:27,069 --> 00:17:29,560
