240
00:17:29,800 --> 00:17:30,950
I am Chasing.

241
00:17:32,070 --> 00:17:34,800
You are League.

242
00:17:35,560 --> 00:17:38,000
I'd be brain-damaged to ask you two for help.

243
00:17:38,070 --> 00:17:38,760
Hurry.

244
00:17:38,920 --> 00:17:40,190
Don't rush.

245
00:17:40,520 --> 00:17:42,110
I have already learned

246
00:17:43,280 --> 00:17:46,040
that members of the Anime Club are going to participate

247
00:17:46,400 --> 00:17:48,520
in a Comic-con in Huai City.

248
00:17:49,280 --> 00:17:54,190
And there is a great amusement park in Huai City.

249
00:17:54,950 --> 00:17:56,190
Amusement park, great idea.

250
00:17:56,430 --> 00:17:57,000
You see.

251
00:17:57,000 --> 00:17:59,710
