257
00:18:11,160 --> 00:18:12,350
I am out now.

258
00:18:17,710 --> 00:18:18,400
Boss.

259
00:18:20,000 --> 00:18:21,590
Are you still chasing love now?

260
00:18:24,190 --> 00:18:25,070
Yes.

261
00:18:29,920 --> 00:18:30,710
Come in.

262
00:18:34,190 --> 00:18:34,830
Mr. Su.

263
00:18:34,830 --> 00:18:36,880
About the science expo of Robot Competition in Huai City,

264
00:18:36,950 --> 00:18:38,190
