265
00:18:38,430 --> 00:18:39,310
Please take a look.

266
00:18:46,350 --> 00:18:47,950
Have you booked the ticket to Huai City?

267
00:18:48,110 --> 00:18:49,800
Yes, nine o'clock tomorrow night.

268
00:18:53,800 --> 00:18:54,830
Reschedule it to the morning.

269
00:18:55,310 --> 00:18:56,070
Okay.

270
00:19:03,760 --> 00:19:04,280
Thanks.

271
00:19:04,640 --> 00:19:05,830
