275
00:19:11,310 --> 00:19:13,350
That's okay. I am free, anyway.

276
00:19:13,470 --> 00:19:15,190
I just took it as a free trip.

277
00:19:15,230 --> 00:19:16,400
Alright, then I should get on first.

278
00:19:16,470 --> 00:19:17,110
Hurry.

279
00:19:20,590 --> 00:19:21,800
Good morning, Lou Feng.

280
00:19:23,710 --> 00:19:25,710
Do you know why the head of the Anime Club

281
00:19:25,830 --> 00:19:26,920
doesn't come this time?

282
